# 统一行尾：源码一律以 LF 入库并检出，消除跨平台 CRLF 噪声与
# Windows 下 autocrlf 带来的「LF will be replaced by CRLF」告警。
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 原生脚本保持 CRLF。
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf

# 二进制资源不做行尾/文本转换。
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.dmg binary
*.exe binary
